<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="31" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="12" pageNumber="31">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="12" pageNumber="31">Elytral surface smooth, striae complete, impunctate, 4 setiferous punctures in interval 3, humeri square, sides subparallel. Pronotum notably cordiform. Size given by Putzeys as 4.5 mm.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
